This is the receiver_node-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the receiver_node blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'receiver_node', which is imported as:

    import receiver_node

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(receiver_node)
